videos.headline: Razorbacks take the lead on 39-yard score
videos.description: Quarterback Ty Storey connects with his tight end Cheyenne O'Grady for a 39-yard for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Arkansas RB goes 69-yards to the house
videos.description: Rakeem Boyd breaks loose and runs 69-yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB draw results in a TD
videos.description: Ole Miss' Jordan Ta'amu keeps it himself and runs in an 18-yard score to cut Arkansas' lead to 17-10.

videos.headline: Razorbacks go deep for 39-yard TD catch
videos.description: Cole Kelley goes long to La'Michael Pettway for a 39-yard touchdown

videos.headline: Ole Miss strikes before halftime
videos.description: Ole Miss' Jordan Ta'amu finds DaMarkus Lodge in tghe end zone for a 6-yard score.

videos.headline: Rebels' WR breaks a tackle and goes 66-yards for a score
videos.description: Wide out Octavious Cooley gets loose and goes 66-yards for a touchdown to make the score 30-24.

videos.headline: Ole Miss takes the lead late against Arkansas
videos.description: Scottie Phillips runs up the middle for a 5-yard score to give the Rebels a 37-33 lead against Arkansas.
